title: MacX DVD Ripper Pro 4.5.9 (Mac OSX)
description:
From MacTake.com

MacX DVD Ripper Pro is an ultimate solution that allows you to rip any DVD movies to video files in all sort of formats for playback on Mac, iPhone/5, iPad/iPad 2/iPad 3, iPod, iPad mini, Apple TV, Android, HTC, Samsung, XOOM, Galaxy Tab, PSP, Surface, etc. It supports ripping DVD to MP4, H.264, MOV, FLV, MPEG, M4V, AVI, QT(QuickTime) with high quality video/audio. The DVD-Backup feature lets you copy DVD to single video file with original video quality and 5.1 channel AC3/DTS Dolby audio. It gives you the ability of trimming video segment, crop frame size, merge video files, extract audio add external subtitle to customize video.


		
WHAT'S NEW
Version 4.5.9:

- Added new profiles for iPhone 6s/Plus, the new Apple TV, iPad Pro, iPad Mini 4, Galaxy Note 5, Galaxy S6 Edge+, Xperia Z5/Z4/C4/M4
- Optimized the output profile interface
- Fixed some minor bugs
